data.description: Property is active contingent. Sellers are accepting back up offers with showings and open houses.  Property is on a premium corner lot with plenty of space and potential RV parking. Garage has 50 amp sub panel with 240 outlet, overhead lighting and storage cabinets.  Sellers have kept the home well maintained. Family oriented area with high school, middle school and elementary less than a mile from site. Exterior siding with stucco under. Commercial shopping within a mile or two not limited to Costco, Walmart, Target, and Home Depot. Matching all new remote ceiling fans. Wood flooring throughout, including master bedroom. The other two bedrooms are carpeted. Auto sprinklers in the backyard, not in front. Kitchen and bathroom are tile matching. Spare tile in garage. Wood-burning insert fireplace. Kitchen has serving window.
